right at that point.

00:08:28.110 --> 00:08:31.900
You can almost view that I'm
pivoting around this point, at

00:08:31.900 --> 00:08:35.850
the intersection of this point
and the plane and the cone.

00:08:35.850 --> 00:08:37.750
Well this now, the
intersection, would look

00:08:37.750 --> 00:08:39.470
something like this.

00:08:39.470 --> 00:08:41.230
It would look like that.

00:08:41.230 --> 00:08:42.490
And it would keep going down.

00:08:42.490 --> 00:08:44.980
So if I were to draw it,
it would look like this.

00:08:44.980 --> 00:08:46.840
If I was right above the
