It pops and it turns
into a parabola.

00:09:17.400 --> 00:09:19.190
So you can kind of view
a parabola-- there is

00:09:19.190 --> 00:09:20.470
this relationship.

00:09:20.470 --> 00:09:23.550
Parabola is what happens when
one side of an ellipse pops

00:09:23.550 --> 00:09:25.580
open and you get this parabola.

